241 copy of the clinical data collected for each consenting client
242 to the board upon request.
243 (l)(k) A licensed midwife shall report to the Alabama
244 Department of Public Health pursuant to Chapter 11A, of Title
245 22, and any other law that requires hospitals or physicians to
246 report to the Alabama Department of Public Health.
247 (m)(l) A licensed midwife shall provide all information
248 required to be provided to new mothers pursuant to Section
249 22-20-3.1, and all information required to be provided to new
250 mothers before discharge by hospitals, as defined in Section
251 22-21-20.
252 (n)(m) A licensed midwife shall order those tests,
